{"tid":2282064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【政情】建制指京官睇直播難忍拉布　人大出手特區即「落刀」","createTime":"2020-11-11T14:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T23:40:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5b11a3965f00007201871f7ca87575f558dede","tid":2282064,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"政圈風聲醞釀幾日，人大常委會決定揭盅四名原定成功過渡的議員由得變唔得。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府在人大常委會公布決定後十分鐘，隨即宣布「開刀」DQ，比起2016年釋法的決定，要待法庭決定，今次「即時死亡」連建制派亦感意外，但決定隻字不提「拉布戰」，令建制派私下有不同演繹。<br />\n<br />\n多名建制派透露，中聯辦在人大公布決定前透過不同方式向他們預告決定內容，有建制派相信要求四名不符參選資格的議員離任，較為合理及易獲公眾接受，但認為議會近期陷於癱瘓是引發決定的導火線。<br />\n<br />\n有建制派更聲稱，有領導人曾觀看立法會直播，覺得拉布情況相當過分，忍無可忍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=412538\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412538&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=9c9c4ee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412538&h=160ce9b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=412538</a>"},{"pid":"f0ab1e4810f6fe381667bf30499ed22438dba586","tid":2282064,"uid":161726,"like":137,"dislike":5,"score":132,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"On 9<br />\n邊有官會睇立法會直播架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講大話講好D 呀"},{"pid":"5e086f7e4814dd2a71734e0e3966c26f87410b84","tid":2282064,"uid":291626,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"梗係難忍 d貪污工程卡死左 搞到無油水進帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6ea839dd6ba8bd181fcbe4f8ef604c80267b2f","tid":2282064,"uid":34869,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"f0ab1e4810f6fe381667bf30499ed22438dba586","tid":2282064,"uid":161726,"like":137,"dislike":5,"score":132,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T14:36:14.000Z","msg":"On 9<br />\n邊有官會睇立法會直播架<img